### Login as user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login as admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Access protected ping endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/protected/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Get current profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Update profile and verify XSS sanitization
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "<script>alert('xss')</script>Alice",
  "bio": "<img src=x onerror=alert('xss')>secure bio"
}

### Verify sanitized profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Admin query with safe filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users?email=example&role=USER&sortBy=username&direction=asc&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin audit endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/audit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Trigger login failures
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### Trigger rate limit by repeating this request quickly
GET http://localhost:8080/api/protected/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Check Prometheus metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus

### Check custom failure metric
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/metrics/security.auth.failure.total
